{"tid":1962153,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沈旭暉 : 「香港人」推廣不到  反被冒充為「一國」漂白","createTime":"2020-04-07T09:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:42:27.000Z","uid":21470,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5521c0554d63331d7cd234ea3bdce7da2ef82f5e","tid":1962153,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:36:59.000Z","msg":"堅離地城：沈旭暉國際生活台 Simon's Glos World<br />\n<br />\n【圖解Condom】<br />\n1.「一國自己人」有用時，香港就「不是」中國，鳳凰衛視就係「香港媒體」，陳馮富珍就係「前港英公務員」，「一國原則評論員」邱騰華會失蹤<br />\n2. 真香港人發聲時，香港就等如港獨，屈小姐湯大狀就會出現<br />\n3. 香港作為一個brand，在國際社會依然有剩餘價值，100%係因為有真香港人捍衛核心價值，例如香港電台記者正常發問<br />\n4. 結果香港人既努力幫唔到自己，反而只幫到「一國」漂白<br />\n#完 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fGVn75i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfGVn75i.jpg&h=1196022a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=3169345373099591&amp;set=a.224514904249334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%3Ffbid%3D3169345373099591%26set%3Da.224514904249334&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=34c7e015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo?fbid=3169345373099591&amp;set=a.224514904249334</a>"},{"pid":"7b9dd7091005be01f20f6855cb18e8526d288f94","tid":1962153,"uid":146030,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:38:31.000Z","msg":"condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國際孤兒你估流架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4931261d0a81734d71a588f1575a0a4488a70cc0","tid":1962153,"uid":31215,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T09:47:49.000Z","msg":"係時候又發揮香港人最強本領<br />\n嗌救命嗌到全世界都知<br />\n鳳凰衛視不是香港傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf8bf1fc6543